WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 20=

00:00:27.660 --> 00:00:28.419
Your Highness,

00:00:28.420 --> 00:00:31.500
isn't there
a more decent way to do this?

00:00:32.300 --> 00:00:33.379
Listen to Suisui.

00:00:33.380 --> 00:00:34.700
Then at least have Suisui...

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.859
find me something that fits.

00:00:37.860 --> 00:00:38.979
Oh,

00:00:38.980 --> 00:00:40.579
just make do with it for now.

00:00:40.580 --> 00:00:43.300
What man looks right
in women's clothes anyway?

00:00:43.660 --> 00:00:44.379
Besides,

00:00:44.380 --> 00:00:46.140
who told you to be built like that?

00:00:46.700 --> 00:00:48.620
Crow, let's go. Lead the way.

00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:04.779
So annoying.

00:01:04.780 --> 00:01:07.300
This couple seems pretty affectionate.

00:01:16.380 --> 00:01:18.179
(Lady Liu, Ning Huchen's cousin)
Why did it go out?

00:01:18.180 --> 00:01:20.139
(Ning Huchen,
Prince of Zhenbei of Tianxuan Kingdom)

00:01:20.140 --> 00:01:20.860
Don't be scared.

00:01:21.700 --> 00:01:23.140
I'll relight it.

00:01:25.500 --> 00:01:26.819
Ning,

00:01:26.820 --> 00:01:29.259
I am the Goddess of Fertility.

00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:30.379
Seeing how devoted you've been

00:01:30.380 --> 00:01:32.099
in praying for a child all these years,

00:01:32.100 --> 00:01:34.620
I have come to bless you.

00:01:35.780 --> 00:01:37.140
What terrible luck.

00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:38.299
Master,

00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:39.819
we're in the middle of something here.

00:01:39.820 --> 00:01:41.499
And this fertility goddess

00:01:41.500 --> 00:01:42.779
just had to drop someone else's child

00:01:42.780 --> 00:01:43.739
into my room?

00:01:43.740 --> 00:01:44.419
Goodness.

00:01:44.420 --> 00:01:46.020
It's actually a pair of secret lovers.

00:01:46.700 --> 00:01:48.380
He's a man?

00:01:48.780 --> 00:01:50.180
Who?

00:01:50.300 --> 00:01:52.100
Who dares make a fool of me?

00:01:53.540 --> 00:01:54.780
Suisui, run!

00:01:58.620 --> 00:02:00.020
Don't run!

00:02:00.580 --> 00:02:01.659
Wait!

00:02:01.660 --> 00:02:03.420
Stop right there!

00:02:07.220 --> 00:02:09.900
A gift from the Young Mistress.
No need to thank me.

00:02:11.900 --> 00:02:13.019
Bird droppings.

00:02:13.020 --> 00:02:14.940
Ugh!

00:02:21.380 --> 00:02:24.899
Little Princess, your plan
doesn't seem too reliable.

00:02:24.900 --> 00:02:28.140
We almost got ourselves killed.

00:02:28.300 --> 00:02:29.259
It's fine.

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:32.619
Later, I'll have Uncle Shiwan
stew a chicken for you to recover.

00:02:32.620 --> 00:02:33.620
Really?

00:02:33.820 --> 00:02:34.779
Mm, really.

00:02:34.780 --> 00:02:35.980
Then I want two.

00:02:40.580 --> 00:02:41.379
Young Mistress,

00:02:41.380 --> 00:02:42.459
we've found out everything.

00:02:42.460 --> 00:02:43.300
Speak.

00:02:43.380 --> 00:02:45.219
That woman is Ning Huchen's cousin.

00:02:45.220 --> 00:02:46.779
The two grew up together.

00:02:46.780 --> 00:02:49.260
He only married Madam Ning
for her money.

00:02:50.100 --> 00:02:51.859
What a shameless opportunist.

00:02:51.860 --> 00:02:53.279
I bet he never wanted

00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:54.499
his wife to get pregnant.

00:02:54.500 --> 00:02:57.820
He only wants to stay together
with his precious cousin.

00:02:58.180 --> 00:02:58.779
Exactly.

00:02:58.780 --> 00:02:59.819
And Madam Ning's

00:02:59.820 --> 00:03:01.419
dowry, shops, and estates

00:03:01.420 --> 00:03:02.459
are all under his name.

00:03:02.460 --> 00:03:04.500
Once Madam Ning dies,
he'll make a fortune.

00:03:05.620 --> 00:03:07.339
I didn't expect this.

00:03:07.340 --> 00:03:08.409
I thought

00:03:08.410 --> 00:03:11.370
Ning Huchen and his wife
were deeply in love.

00:03:11.580 --> 00:03:12.499
Suisui,

00:03:12.500 --> 00:03:13.620
remember this.

00:03:13.780 --> 00:03:16.179
You must never run off
with a bad man in the future.

00:03:16.180 --> 00:03:17.300
Got it?

00:03:18.300 --> 00:03:21.900
Father, I'm still little.

00:03:22.020 --> 00:03:26.140
Aren't you worrying a bit too early?

00:03:28.300 --> 00:03:31.099
We even had the little ants
deliver a message to Madam Ning.

00:03:31.100 --> 00:03:33.540
Madam Ning must still be waiting for us.

00:03:33.980 --> 00:03:36.119
Looks like this time,

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:39.940
Madam Ning's hopes will be crushed.

00:03:45.460 --> 00:03:46.420
Madam.

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:49.600
(Madam Ning, wife of the Prince
of Zhenbei of Tianxuan Kingdom)

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:55.360
I've been taking this medicine
for so long.

00:03:57.700 --> 00:03:59.420
Maybe there's no point anymore.

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:06.040
(Do not miss today's chance.)

00:04:06.900 --> 00:04:08.020
This...

00:04:09.580 --> 00:04:11.300
Am I seeing things?

00:04:13.500 --> 00:04:14.820
Hahaha!

00:04:15.860 --> 00:04:17.140
Madam Ning.

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:28.119
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:31.959
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:04:31.960 --> 00:04:35.479
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:38.440
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:42.959
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:46.720
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:50.119
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:54.160
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:04:59.760 --> 00:05:03.439
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:07.079
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:10.799
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:14.439
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:14.440 --> 00:05:18.119
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:18.120 --> 00:05:20.039
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:26.240
♪Good fortune♪